; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/st-util.md

% st-util, common

# Run GDB server on port 4500
st-util <__p___listen_port_> <4500>

# [Interactive] Connect to GDB server within `gdb`
target extended-remote <localhost>:<4500>

# [Interactive] Write firmware to device
load <firmware_elf>
